IY4GINVCOSTWEIGHT(IY411,IGKFIND) = SUM(Y$(IY411(Y) AND (YVALUE(Y) GE YVALUE(IY411))), IDISCOUNTFACTOR(Y));!! Hans 20150205; TODO: missing that some G will reach lifetime inside iy411, cf. IY4GREMAINY above, TODO
